I"y<p>Six By Six is delighted to announce that they will be staging  their second event and exhibition.  </p>

<p>The evening will consist of the opening of an exhibition of  Colin McPherson’s photography from his long-term project Berlin: After the Wall which documents the city’s changing  landscape over the last three decades. There will be short talks and presentations on a number of subjects relevant to the work on show. </p>

<p>All welcome, admission is free.</p>

